<div id="review_3218873499" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3218873499" />
    <a title="C. Hale" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/110986112-c-hale"><img alt="C. Hale" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1583418115p2/110986112.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3218873499?book_show_action=true">Mar 05, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="C. Hale" class="user" itemprop="url" name="C. Hale" href="/user/show/110986112-c-hale">C. Hale</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3218873499" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8847408940746171343"><b> One Word...LEGENDARY</b><br/><br/>THE LEGENDARY WOLF delivers a gritty and action-packed narrative of a violent assassin who has grown old and lost his way. It&apos;s a modern-day redemption story following our protagonist, Grayson Wolf. Even with that, it does not lose its charm of establishing a strong foundation for Grayson. The book showcases his evolution from a man who has been in hiding and hates himself before turning back into a top-notch assassin as he recalls his violent skills and instincts honed with</span>
  <span id="freeText8847408940746171343" style="display:none"><b> One Word...LEGENDARY</b><br /><br />THE LEGENDARY WOLF delivers a gritty and action-packed narrative of a violent assassin who has grown old and lost his way. It's a modern-day redemption story following our protagonist, Grayson Wolf. Even with that, it does not lose its charm of establishing a strong foundation for Grayson. The book showcases his evolution from a man who has been in hiding and hates himself before turning back into a top-notch assassin as he recalls his violent skills and instincts honed with years and years of training and operating in high stress situations.<br /><br />The action sequences are close and dirty, with Grayson's employing skillful and unforgiving measures to take out his opponents. The hand to hand fight sequences highlight Grayson's close quarter combat skills. The gun fights and shootouts are in no short supply, with firearms being an extension of Grayson rather than separate mechanisms. <br /><br />Grayson is soon in the care of a young girl he must protect. Though it seems odd at first, the girl represents Grayson's second chance, and she symbolizes the innocence and beauty that he never got to feel in life. She is the crux of his redemption. I enjoyed their dynamic and found their relationship to be an essential part of the story, driving the narrative forward rather than simply a existing as a filler.<br /><br />I would definitely recommend this action thriller to fans of the genre, especially those who wish to experience an excellent action/thriller that'll take you for a great ride </span>
  <a data-text-id="8847408940746171343" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


