  <span id="freeText12601196445491419584" style="display:none"><b> Amazing story! </b><br /><br />Grayson Wolf is a man who has sunken lower than any man can. He is broken and is a soldier who has no battle left to fight. The story opens with him drinking away the rest of his life and haunted by his demons. That is until he is suddenly thrust into the middle of another war that he does not even understand. <br /><br />This novel is outstanding. The characters are well-written and you can feel what they feel. The character of Grayson and the writing from his point-of-view is especially great, and the story just pulls you in. This is the kind of story fans of the genre are always looking for, and it is definitely worth a read!</span>
