<span id="freeTextContainer15794131835550313006"><b> <i>The Legendary Wolf</i></b> is Habib&apos;s finest written book, yet. I was blown away by the emotional impact of Heart of Aleppo, and Habib continues with more of the same gravitas with his latest book. All of this is interwoven through absolutely brutal action sequences that continue topping each other all the way up to the blood soaked finale. I couldn&apos;t put it down, guzzling it down page after page in less than a day!<br/></span>
  <span id="freeText15794131835550313006" style="display:none"><b> <i>The Legendary Wolf</i></b> is Habib's finest written book, yet. I was blown away by the emotional impact of Heart of Aleppo, and Habib continues with more of the same gravitas with his latest book. All of this is interwoven through absolutely brutal action sequences that continue topping each other all the way up to the blood soaked finale. I couldn't put it down, guzzling it down page after page in less than a day!<br /></span>
