<span id="freeTextContainer2086586220258425791">The book is an action/thriller with a strong western flair. It follows Grayson Wolf, a former government assassin. He was the greatest killer in the world decades ago. But after going AWOL on his government before butchering the vice president and countless other officials one night, he has been living underground for nearly 25 or 30 years now. He spends every moment haunted by his demons and his past. When the story opens, Grayson has now grown old and is a shell of the man he once was. He is b</span>
  <span id="freeText2086586220258425791" style="display:none">The book is an action/thriller with a strong western flair. It follows Grayson Wolf, a former government assassin. He was the greatest killer in the world decades ago. But after going AWOL on his government before butchering the vice president and countless other officials one night, he has been living underground for nearly 25 or 30 years now. He spends every moment haunted by his demons and his past. When the story opens, Grayson has now grown old and is a shell of the man he once was. He is borderline suicidal, and he tries to take his own life every night. That all changes when an old comrade shows up on his front door. The comrade needs help protecting a young girl from the dark forces pursuing her, and Grayson is reluctantly pulled into all this. Unknown to him, this is his chance at redemption!<br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="2086586220258425791" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
