<span id="freeTextContainer13287629819480705796">The novel is meaningful while entertaining. Readers who enjoy character-driven thrillers will love this story. Grayson Wolf was once the greatest government agent the world had ever seen, and he was an expert/experienced killer. Now he is an old man living underground after having gone AWOL on his government decades ago. Grayson is a shadow of the assassin he once was. <br/><br/>He get&apos;s his second chance in this story, an opportunity to finally defeat the monsters he chained up inside of him. The novel i</span>
  <span id="freeText13287629819480705796" style="display:none">The novel is meaningful while entertaining. Readers who enjoy character-driven thrillers will love this story. Grayson Wolf was once the greatest government agent the world had ever seen, and he was an expert/experienced killer. Now he is an old man living underground after having gone AWOL on his government decades ago. Grayson is a shadow of the assassin he once was. <br /><br />He get's his second chance in this story, an opportunity to finally defeat the monsters he chained up inside of him. The novel is a thrill ride that is fast-paced and packed with action. However, the best part about this is not the bloody action or chases. It's the character of Grayson himself. It's the story of a man who must overcome his greatest obstacle: his own self. </span>
