        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2957142336" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15361452548898136728">I wasn’t sure if I would like this one, to be honest. It sounded interesting enough and I love the thriller aspect to it. I’m so glad that I did read this! It was a great one!<br/><br/>This is a fast paced thrill ride of ups, downs, twists and turns. From one page to the next you are following Grayson and feeling the heart pounding intensity that he feels. The military feel to this is incredible, the suspense if phenomenal.<br/><br/>Part movie feel, part novel feel, Grayson’s story will leave you begging for more. </span>
  <span id="freeText15361452548898136728" style="display:none">I wasn’t sure if I would like this one, to be honest. It sounded interesting enough and I love the thriller aspect to it. I’m so glad that I did read this! It was a great one!<br /><br />This is a fast paced thrill ride of ups, downs, twists and turns. From one page to the next you are following Grayson and feeling the heart pounding intensity that he feels. The military feel to this is incredible, the suspense if phenomenal.<br /><br />Part movie feel, part novel feel, Grayson’s story will leave you begging for more. I am so glad that I gave this 4 star novel a chance and I am excited to read more work from this highly talented author!<br /><br />*I received a complimentary copy of this book from Publisher and was under no obligation to post a review, positive or negative.*</span>
