              <span id="reviewTextContainer2919836786" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10217435744746821206">Great read for fans of redemption stories! Though the whole atonement/redemption arc can be seen as cliche, Habib intertwines those themes into THE LEGENDARY WOLF marvelously! Grayson is the perfect character for this story. Though he has such a mysterious and harrowed past, it is not hard to relate to him because his personal struggles are things that most people have gone through to a certain extent. This novel also has a lot of re-read value, and you&apos;ll pick up a ton of new details on the 2nd</span>
  <span id="freeText10217435744746821206" style="display:none">Great read for fans of redemption stories! Though the whole atonement/redemption arc can be seen as cliche, Habib intertwines those themes into THE LEGENDARY WOLF marvelously! Grayson is the perfect character for this story. Though he has such a mysterious and harrowed past, it is not hard to relate to him because his personal struggles are things that most people have gone through to a certain extent. This novel also has a lot of re-read value, and you'll pick up a ton of new details on the 2nd and 3rd reads (I'm speaking out of experience here lol). </span>
  <a data-text-id="10217435744746821206" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


