<div id="review_2974604148" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2974604148" />
    <a title="B. Giovanni" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/102648483-b-giovanni"><img alt="B. Giovanni" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1568293948p2/102648483.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2974604148?book_show_action=true">Sep 12, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="B. Giovanni" class="user" itemprop="url" name="B. Giovanni" href="/user/show/102648483-b-giovanni">B. Giovanni</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/102648483-b-giovanni?shelf=action">action</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/102648483-b-giovanni?shelf=thriller">thriller</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/102648483-b-giovanni?shelf=military-fiction">military-fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/102648483-b-giovanni?shelf=fast-paced">fast-paced</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/102648483-b-giovanni?shelf=2019">2019</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/102648483-b-giovanni?shelf=5-star">5-star</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/102648483-b-giovanni?shelf=character-focused">character-focused</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/102648483-b-giovanni?shelf=kindle">kindle</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/102648483-b-giovanni?shelf=new-author">new-author</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2974604148" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6304753525432414747">A classic redemption story with a modern twist -- just as the premise promised! I was pulled into Grayson Wolf&apos;s shadowy world from the first page. What followed was a plot full of twist and turns as Grayson is forced to face his demons and rise into the hero he once was. The story has so much gravitas that you can&apos;t turn away. It&apos;s a perfect blend of characters, plot, and amazing action sequences. I noticed a lot of the symbolism, extended metaphors, and themes the author incorporates into the </span>
  <span id="freeText6304753525432414747" style="display:none">A classic redemption story with a modern twist -- just as the premise promised! I was pulled into Grayson Wolf's shadowy world from the first page. What followed was a plot full of twist and turns as Grayson is forced to face his demons and rise into the hero he once was. The story has so much gravitas that you can't turn away. It's a perfect blend of characters, plot, and amazing action sequences. I noticed a lot of the symbolism, extended metaphors, and themes the author incorporates into the story, and it made it all the more better.</span>
  <a data-text-id="6304753525432414747" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


