        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2827640271" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15230499648177708007">The story is really good.<br/>The characters are very interesting.<br/>The action scenes are FREAKING BAD-A**! Habib puts both an extremely interesting story and lots of great action in one novel and it’s better than most (though not all) stories I’d say.<br/>This story is never predictable.<br/>The ending is great.<br/><br/>Overall:<br/>Great novel for sure! I highly recommend it for people who like bad-a** hero stuff!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


